.TH systemd-swap 8 "JUNE 2020" "systemd-swap 4.2.1" systemd-swap
.SH NAME
systemd-swap \- Script for creating hybrid swap space from zram swaps, swap files and swap partitions.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B systemd-swap [-h]
.I start|stop|status
.SH DESCRIPTION
Systemd-swap manages the configuration of
.B zram
and
.B zswap
and allows for automatically setting up swap files through
.B swapfc
and automatically enables available swapfiles and swap partitions.
.SH OPTIONS
.IP start
Starts systemd-swap.
.IP stop
Stops systemd-swap.
.IP status
Prints the status of systemd-swap; modules being used and their statuses.
